name: Woke Chain
description: Woke Chain is not just a cryptocurrency, it's a movement. The perfect blend of satire, humor, and financial opportunity. With a supply of 823,900,000... $GOWOKE is about ensuring inclusivity and everyone getting their fair share, while leveraging the speed and power of Solana Blockchain to create the best user experience.
